{"tid":981892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普預測：美中將達成協議 結束貿易戰","createTime":"2019-01-14T15:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T04:20:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b541cda97c5846bd1cce28037d649d433353c45c","tid":981892,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:48:50.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普今天預測，美國將與中國達成協議，結束貿易戰。<br />\n<br />\n川普指出，中方要求談判，而且美中雙方談判進行順利。<br />\n<br />\n川普在白宮向記者做了以上表示。<br />\n<br />\n川普已揚言，如果中方未能針對竊取智慧財產權、強迫技術轉移、以及其他非關稅壁壘進行改善，他將在3月2日針對價值2000億美元的中國進口商品增加關稅。<br />\n<br />\n美中上週在北京進行中階談判，這是川普和中國國家主席習近平去年12月在布宜諾斯艾利斯同意貿易戰休兵90天以來，美中雙方首次面對面進行磋商。<br />\n<br />\n美國財政部長梅努欽（Steven Mnuchin）告訴記者，中方首席談判代表國務院副總理劉鶴本月稍後可能訪問華盛頓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201901140334.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201901140334.aspx&d=Kj2VNr%2Fz%2FzEZPka8Htoob9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=8b116b6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201901140334.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"424d671ddfd1d105aa7ea4c79c359e782872a22c","tid":981892,"uid":1654,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:49:13.000Z","msg":"put 得"},{"pid":"f308ed0bd0c97ee90f0643d85ead4e287d752a53","tid":981892,"uid":57787,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:58:33.000Z","msg":"佢無講幾時，可能係支那亡國之前達成都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8d6f05baca7cb2ff9929118a89897ca92d35dd","tid":981892,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:59:09.000Z","msg":"中美和好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c07d4fe96a2846b4839dbbfedd0f24b7647355","tid":981892,"uid":39200,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T16:01:44.000Z","msg":"攪到加仔唔上唔落仲要有人被判死刑，轉頭自己又話同大陸傾掂數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6183092ef1eb169bd5a6bec90feccf